snippet.title: Top Gun Fire at Will gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Top Gun Fire at Will, Dos PC game produced by MicroProse in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/top-gun-fire-at-will/1202/
Playing as Maverick in a couple of missions. Great dogfighting game with direct reference to the movie.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Top Gun Danger Zone - https://youtu.be/Bwa-mDnUNz0
Lock-On - https://youtu.be/ZVo-8DZsDF0
Empire! - https://youtu.be/nY7BbU4pX6M
